TEAM EFFICIENCY (0-1.0 points)\n  * How significantly will this reduce attorney or staff workload?\n  * Does it eliminate repetitive tasks that cause burnout?\n  * Will it enable our team to focus on higher-value activities?\n  * Does it reduce stress while maintaining quality?\n\n4. TECHNICAL FEASIBILITY (0-1.0 points)\n  * Can this be implemented with our existing technology stack?\n  * How well does it integrate with our Airtable-centric workflow?\n  * Are the required AI capabilities (GPT, Claude, etc.) mature enough?\n  * What is the complexity level? (Lower complexity = higher score)\n\n5. STRATEGIC INNOVATION (0-1.0 points)\n  * Does this automation position us ahead of competing law firms?\n  * Will it create a \"wow factor\" for clients that reinforces our premium positioning?\n  * Does it lay groundwork for future automation capabilities?\n  * Is this a first-mover advantage in the legal industry?\n\nPRIORITY LEVELS:\n5.0 -
